{"word":"Ahaziah","slug":"ahaziah","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Ahaziah</b> - <b>(a)</b> King of Judah, also called Azariah, or Jehoahaz, son of Jehoram<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=8&verse=25'>2Ki 8:25</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=9&verse=16'>2Ki 9:16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=9&verse=23'>2Ki 9:23</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=9&verse=27'>2Ki 9:27</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=22&verse=2'>2Ch 22:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=22&verse=9'>2Ch 22:9</a><p/><b>(b)</b> King of Israel, son of Ahab<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=22&verse=40'>1Ki 22:40</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=22&verse=52'>1Ki 22:52</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=1&verse=2'>2Ki 1:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=1&verse=17'>2Ki 1:17</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=20&verse=35'>2Ch 20:35</a>"}]}